webResources.textAttributionSnippet: (en) "Group of mushroom animals, sea anemones, hives and mussels on a bag at dock. Text on the back: “Wharf-pile group. Discloses the numerous sponges, hydroids, sea-anemones, shell-fish and other inactive animals with the arrow of an abandonment wharf are crowded the low water mark.”: Composed with photon. 2941-2954. See also series with photon. 2930-2940 with postcards partly the same motif, non-coloured.' - https://www.europeana.eu/item/52/gnm_photo_GNM2938_001. Göteborgs naturhistoriska museum - http://digitaltmuseum.se/021015942708. CC BY - http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.5/
